{"tid":422654,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我媽沖左杯日本高級茶話同我慶中秋","createTime":"2017-10-03T09:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T09:11:15.000Z","uid":74595,"like":1135,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"6936a0f65837154434b2737f7c2f032f89d5a63b","tid":422654,"uid":74595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我媽同我講沖左茶<br />\n話係乜朋友係日本買既手信<br />\n高級野 自己未飲都叫我飲先。<br />\n我一睇 頂你杯茶白色既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/164638_2385201a12d6cbdb900d505c2c8aa097.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F164638_2385201a12d6cbdb900d505c2c8aa097.jpg&h=455d830e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過我有既係冒險家精神<br />\n儘管一試 應該唔差得去邊既<br />\n結果個味好似溝左水既奶咁<br />\n難飲到飲左一啖就頂唔順<br />\n<br />\n我唯有問佢拎盒茶睇睇<br />\n嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/165220_5e41f508a5064b608ee749825114d416.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F165220_5e41f508a5064b608ee749825114d416.jpg&h=2fd2e596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/03/165558_104afc0988bccd34fb4abe96cce392c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F03%2F165558_104afc0988bccd34fb4abe96cce392c9.jpg&h=aa9ea5c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來係餅乾 俾佢當茶沖<br />\n佢重話以為係茶餅 要用手捽碎<br />\n佢朋友又唔識睇 我媽又唔識睇<br />\n我媽媽實在太可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebd46a43dd8